{
  "page": "Lord Cressey",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cressey\" title=\"House Cressey\"><img alt=\"House Cressey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Cressey.svg/50px-House_Cressey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Cressey.svg/75px-House_Cressey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/House_Cressey.svg/100px-House_Cressey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Cressey</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cressey\" title=\"House Cressey\"><img alt=\"House Cressey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Cressey.svg/50px-House_Cressey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Cressey.svg/75px-House_Cressey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/House_Cressey.svg/100px-House_Cressey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">Lord</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Cressey\" title=\"House Cressey\">House Cressey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Cressey</b> was the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cressey\" title=\"House Cressey\">House Cressey</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Cressey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord Cressey was one of the six <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> who accompanied Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfryd_Mooton\" title=\"Manfryd Mooton\">Manfryd Mooton</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>. As the Crown's envoy, Manfryd was tasked to make peace with the <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord_of_Braavos\" title=\"Sealord of Braavos\">Sealord of Braavos</a> after the recent <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Alyn%27s_attack\" title=\"Lord Alyn&#39;s attack\">conflict</a> between the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_City\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Free City\">Free City</a> and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a>. While Manfryd treated with the Sealord, Lord Cressey spread bribes among the Braavosi <a href=\"/index.php/Keyholders\" title=\"Keyholders\">keyholders</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Magisters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magisters\">magisters</a>, and other notables.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Cressey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403175342\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.117 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.444 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 440/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10451/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4763/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 451/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 735/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.300/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  429.138      1 -total\n 95.96%  411.796      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.27%  408.853      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.88%   46.692     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.08%   21.818      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.98%    8.511      1 Template:Ref\n  1.42%    6.107      1 Template:Date\n  1.37%    5.873      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.53%    2.291      1 Template:References\n 